Fst.mat

function (x) 
{
    if (is.data.frame(x)) 
        x <- as.matrix(x)
    if (!(is.numeric(x) || is.logical(x))) 
        stop("'x' must be numeric")
    ncy <- ncx <- ncol(x)
    r <- matrix(0, nrow = ncx, ncol = ncy)
    for (i in seq_len(ncx)) {
        for (j in seq_len(i)) {
            x2 <- x[, i]
            y2 <- x[, j]
            r[i, j] <- mean(Fst(x2, y2), na.rm = T)
        }
    }
    r <- r + t(r) - diag(diag(r))
    rownames(r) <- colnames(x)
    colnames(r) <- colnames(x)
    r
}

Fst.mat = function (x) 
{
    if (is.data.frame(x)) 
        x <- as.matrix(x)
    if (!(is.numeric(x) || is.logical(x))) 
        stop("'x' must be numeric")
    ncy <- ncx <- ncol(x)
    r <- matrix(0, nrow = ncx, ncol = ncy)
    for (i in seq_len(ncx)) {
        for (j in seq_len(i)) {
            x2 <- x[, i]
            y2 <- x[, j]
            r[i, j] <- mean(Fst(x2, y2), na.rm = T)
        }
    }
    r <- r + t(r) - diag(diag(r))
    rownames(r) <- colnames(x)
    colnames(r) <- colnames(x)
    r
}

###MDS Regressions - in accordance w/ S.Greenblum Code
In [8]:
project_points=function(m1,b1,myx,myy){
  m2=-1*1/m1
  b2=myy-m2*myx
  project.x=(b2-b1)/(m1-m2)
  project.y=b1+m1*project.x
  mydist=sqrt(project.x^2 + (project.y-b1)^2)*c(-1,1)[1+as.numeric(project.x>0)];
  return(cbind(project.x,project.y,mydist))
}

df.transformed.exp = data.frame()
for (p in phases){
    mds.p = mds %>% filter(phase == p)
    for (c in cages){ 
        df = mds.p %>% filter(cage == c)
        t0.x = as.numeric(mds %>% filter(cage == c) %>%
            filter(phase %in% c('exp1', 'exp2') & tpt == '0') %>% pull(V1)) #x coordinate of t0
        t0.y = as.numeric(mds %>% filter(cage == c) %>%
            filter(phase %in% c('exp1', 'exp2') & tpt == '0') %>% pull(V2))#y coordinate of t0
        df$translate.x=0
        df$translate.y=0
        df$project.x=0
        df$project.y=0
        df$dist=0
        df = df %>% rename(x = V1, y = V2)
        #translate each point around x/y
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.x = x - t0.x) 
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.y = y - t0.y)
        df.transformed.exp = rbind(df.transformed.exp, df)
        }
}

for (c in cages){
    df.transformed.exp1 = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == 'exp1' & cage == c)
    bf = lm(translate.y ~ translate.x, data = df.transformed.exp1)
    b1=coef(bf)[1]
    m1=coef(bf)[2]
    df.correlations = data.frame()
    for (p in phases){
        df = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == p & cage == c)
        projections=project_points(m1,b1,df$translate.x,df$translate.y)
        df$project.x=projections[,1]
        df$project.y=projections[,2]

        ptc=data.frame(phase = p,cage=c, b1=b1,m1=m1,Cor=cor(df$tpt,df$dist))
        ptc=ptc %>% mutate(Cor = Cor * -1) #phase the correlation in regard to the slope of the original line
        df.correlations = rbind(df.correlations, ptc)
        df.correlations.meta = rbind(df.correlations.meta, df.correlations)
        }
        
    }

##transform data:
#function to get transformed data
transform.data = function(mds.df, chr, Cage){
        df = mds.df %>% filter(chrom == chr & cage == Cage)
        t0.x = as.numeric(df %>%
            filter(tpt == '0') %>% pull(V1)) #x coordinate of t0
        t0.y = as.numeric(df %>% 
            filter(tpt == '0') %>% pull(V2))#y coordinate of t0        
        df$translate.x=0
        df$translate.y=0
        df$project.x=0
        df$project.y=0
        df$dist=0
        df = df %>% rename(x = V1, y = V2)
        #translate each point around x/y
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.x = x - t0.x) 
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.y = y - t0.y)
    df =as.data.frame(df)
    return(df)
    }


#get expansion and truncation transformed data
df.transformed.exp = data.frame()
for (c in as.character(unique(mds.exp$cage))){

        df.transformed.exp = rbind(df.transformed.exp, df.chr.c)  
    }
}

project.data.shuff = function(df.transformed, Cage, Phase, Chr){
    df.transformed.exp1 = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == 'exp1' & cage == Cage & chrom == Chr)
    bf = lm(translate.y ~ translate.x, data = df.transformed.exp1)
    b1=coef(bf)[1]
    m1=coef(bf)[2]
    df = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == Phase & cage == Cage  & chrom == Chr)
    projections=project_points(m1,b1,df$translate.x,df$translate.y)
    df$project.x=projections[,1]
    df$project.y=projections[,2]
    df$dist=projections[,3]
    df = df %>%
          arrange(translate.x) %>%  # Sort by tpt and x columns
          mutate(tpt = sample(tpt))
    df$chrom = Chr
    ptc=data.frame(phase = Phase,cage=Cage,chrom = Chr, b1=b1,m1=m1,Cor=cor(df$tpt,df$dist))
    return(ptc)
}

mds = read.csv('./Fst.MDS.AllSamps.ByChrom.NSitesPowerAnalysis.csv')
mds = mds %>% rowwise() %>% 
   mutate(phase = case_when(phase == 'expansion' & tpt %in% c('0','1','2','3','4') ~ 'exp1',
                            phase == 'expansion' & tpt %in% c('6','7','8','9') ~ 'exp2',
                            phase == 'truncation' ~ 'trunc'))

mds.exp = mds %>% filter(phase %in% c('exp1', 'exp2'))
mds.trunc = mds %>% filter(phase == 'trunc')

##transform data:
#function to get transformed data
transform.data = function(mds.df, chr, Cage){
        df = mds.df %>% filter(chrom == chr & cage == Cage)
        t0.x = as.numeric(df %>%
            filter(tpt == '0') %>% pull(V1)) #x coordinate of t0
        t0.y = as.numeric(df %>% 
            filter(tpt == '0') %>% pull(V2))#y coordinate of t0        
        df$translate.x=0
        df$translate.y=0
        df$project.x=0
        df$project.y=0
        df$dist=0
        df = df %>% rename(x = V1, y = V2)
        #translate each point around x/y
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.x = x - t0.x) 
        df = df %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(translate.y = y - t0.y)
    df =as.data.frame(df)
    return(df)
    }


#get expansion and truncation transformed data
df.transformed.exp = data.frame()
for (c in as.character(unique(mds.exp$cage))){
    for (Chrom in as.character(unique(mds.exp$chrom))){
        df.chr.c = transform.data(mds.exp, chr = Chrom, Cage = c)
        df.transformed.exp = rbind(df.transformed.exp, df.chr.c)  
    }
}
df.transformed.trunc = data.frame()
for (c in as.character(unique(mds.trunc$cage))){
    for (Chrom in as.character(unique(mds.trunc$chrom))){
        df.chr.c = transform.data(mds.trunc, chr = Chrom, Cage = c)
        df.transformed.trunc = rbind(df.transformed.trunc, df.chr.c)  
    }
}

df.transformed.meta = data.frame(rbind(df.transformed.exp, df.transformed.trunc))

project.data.shuff = function(df.transformed, Cage, Phase, Chr){
    df.transformed.exp1 = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == 'exp1' & cage == Cage & chrom == Chr)
    bf = lm(translate.y ~ translate.x, data = df.transformed.exp1)
    b1=coef(bf)[1]
    m1=coef(bf)[2]
    df = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == Phase & cage == Cage  & chrom == Chr)
    projections=project_points(m1,b1,df$translate.x,df$translate.y)
    df$project.x=projections[,1]
    df$project.y=projections[,2]
    df$dist=projections[,3]
    df = df %>%
          arrange(translate.x) %>%  # Sort by tpt and x columns
          mutate(tpt = sample(tpt))
    df$chrom = Chr
    ptc=data.frame(phase = Phase,cage=Cage,chrom = Chr, b1=b1,m1=m1,Cor=cor(df$tpt,df$dist))
    return(ptc)
}

project.data = function(df.transformed, Cage, Phase, Chr){
    df.transformed.exp1 = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == 'exp1' & cage == Cage & chrom == Chr)
    bf = lm(translate.y ~ translate.x, data = df.transformed.exp1)
    b1=coef(bf)[1]
    m1=coef(bf)[2]
    df = df.transformed %>% filter(phase == Phase & cage == Cage  & chrom == Chr)
    projections=project_points(m1,b1,df$translate.x,df$translate.y)
    df$project.x=projections[,1]
    df$project.y=projections[,2]
    df$dist=projections[,3]
    df$chrom = Chr
    ptc=data.frame(phase = Phase,cage=Cage,chrom = Chr, b1=b1,m1=m1,Cor=cor(df$tpt,df$dist))
    return(ptc)
}

    bf = lm(translate.y ~ translate.x, data = df.transformed.exp1)

    m1=coef(bf)[2]

data = data.frame()
for (p in  as.character(unique(df.emp$phase))){
    for (c in as.character(unique(df.emp$chrom))){
        d = df.emp %>% filter(chrom == c & phase == p)
        obs.cor = median(d %>% pull(Cor))
        #obs.cor = abs(obs.cor) #absolute value of correlation
        d.s = df.shuff %>% filter(chrom == c & phase == p)
        shuff.dist = ecdf(d.s$Cor)  #shuffled distribution
        if(obs.cor > 0){
            p.val <- (1 - shuff.dist(obs.cor))
            }else{p.val <- shuff.dist(obs.cor)}
        df.new = cbind(p, c, obs.cor,  p.val)
        data = rbind(data, df.new)
    }
    }

data = unique(data)
data = data %>% filter(p != 'exp1')
